    "Austria and Malaysia each accounted for 10 articles and Serbia's contribution was 16 articles.",
    "Figure 9 provides an illustrative depiction of the nations yielding the highest number of articles.",
    "This study utilized VOSviewer to examine the current status and emerging trends in GeoGebra research within the field of mathematics education.",
    "A total of 340 papers published between 2007 and 2023 were retrieved from the SCOPUS database for analysis.",
    "The aim was to investigate the trends in studies focusing on GeoGebra over this period using bibliometric analysis."
  ]
